    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Formal dedications and settings apart by a cleric or other religious dignitary of buildings, plots of land, or objects for ceremonial or religious purposes. For the bestowings of a sacred office upon a person, use "ordinations."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
